Package database.statement.insert

Class InsertSQLStatement

java.lang.Object
database.statement.insert.InsertSQLStatement
public class InsertSQLStatement extends Object
A helper class used to construct an SQL insert statement. Provides a fluent API with method chaining with the goal of making SQL statements easier to construct.
Version:
1.0 - June 2nd 2023
Author:
Tommy Shan
